#

Seared Scallops with Lemon Butter Sauce and Sautéed Spinach

$30
450 kcal
Difficulty: 60%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePescatarian

Tags:

DinnerGourmetSeafood

Description

Perfectly seared scallops with a tangy lemon butter sauce, complemented by tender sautéed spinach.

Ingredients

  • Scallops: 12 large
  • Unsalted Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves
  • Fresh Spinach: 4 cups
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
